    <text>
    <body>
        <p>Muhlenberg County, Kentucky, attorney. Kentucky native. Married to Maranda Pittman. Father of Tibereas Pittman, Mary E. Pittman, Emma Pittman, Elizabeth Pittman, Collins B. Pittman, and Ruth W. Pittman. Attorney in Muhlenberg County in 1860.</p>

    </body>
